PN,39101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FA teenager who had an "obsession" with
OL,7,FSouthport killer Axel Rudakubana and
OL,8,Fwanted to carry out a copycat attack
OL,9,Fhas avoided a custodial sentence.
OL,11,FThe court heard he had an "obsession"
OL,12,Fwith Southport killer Axel Rudakubana
OL,13,Fand wanted to "re-enact" the attack
OL,14,Fwhich left three girls dead and ten
OL,15,Fpeople injured at a Taylor Swift-
OL,16,Fthemed dance class in July 2024.
OL,18,FMonths before his arrest the white
OL,19,FBritish boy, now 17, visited Southport
OL,20,Fand told a contact on TikTok "77 days
OL,21,Funtil Axel 2".
OL,26,@nD@WOUnD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FThe youth, who cannot be named because
OL,7,Fof his age, had collected four knives
OL,8,Fand a green hoodie similar to the one
OL,9,Fworn by the killer, Liverpool Crown
OL,10,FCourt heard.
OL,12,FThe teenager pleaded guilty in January
OL,13,F2026 to four counts of possessing
OL,14,Finformation likely to be useful to a
OL,15,Fperson planning or committing an act
OL,16,Fof terrorism.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FThe documents, found on his phone,
OL,7,Fincluded an Al Qaida training manual
OL,8,Fwhich was also possessed by Rudakubana
OL,9,Fand instructions for preparing ricin,
OL,10,Fthe poison found in the Southport
OL,11,Fkiller's home after his attack.
OL,13,FJudge Neil Flewitt KC told the court
OL,14,Fit had been a "difficult decision" as
OL,15,Fhe sentenced the boy to a youth
OL,16,Frehabilitation order which will last
OL,17,Fthree years and provide "intensive
OL,18,Fsupervision and surveillance".
OL,20,FHe was also made subject to a three-
OL,21,Fyear criminal behaviour order.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@bO]yD@YOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FThe judge said: "I think that a youth
OL,7,Frehabilitation order will be more
OL,8,Fhelpful to you and will provide more
OL,9,Fprotection for the public than keeping
OL,10,Fon in custody."
OL,12,FIn December last year, while in
OL,13,Fcustody after his arrest, the boy was
OL,14,Frecorded as saying that as soon as he
OL,15,Fgot out he would "go into a primary
OL,16,Fschool" and "little girls" would be
OL,17,Fhis first victims, the judge said.
OL,26,@nD@QOUrD@OO]wD@ROUxD@GO]xD@MOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FThe white teenager appeared to laugh
OL,7,Fand put his head in his hands as Adam
OL,8,FBirkby, prosecuting, read out a note
OL,9,Ffound on the boy's phone in which he
OL,10,Fdescribed Rudakubana as a "hero" and
OL,11,Fsaid: "I love him. He's the one person
OL,12,FI look up to. I felt like he was
OL,13,Fspeaking to me.
OL,15,F"I felt like all these isolated
OL,16,Fincidents were speaking to me to act
OL,17,Fup. He was me. He is the black version
OL,18,Fof me."
OL,26,@rD@[OUrD@`O]sD@GOUwD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FThe court heard that the boy, then
OL,7,Faged 16, told a 999 operator on August
OL,8,F6 last year that he had planned to re-
OL,9,Fenact the Southport attack on the
OL,10,Ffirst anniversary but was not able to
OL,11,Ffind an event close to his home.
OL,13,FHe said the "idea of violence"
OL,14,Fcaptivated him and he had watched "a
OL,15,Fload of Isis videos".
OL,17,FWhen police attended his home he spoke
OL,18,Fabout plans to commit a mass casualty
OL,19,Fattack and of his admiration of
OL,20,FRudakubana, who he said had a similar
OL,21,Finterest in "genocides and that".
OL,26,@uD@MOUuD@^O]vD@cOUwD@TO]}D@MOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FHe was twice referred to the Prevent
OL,7,Fcounter-terrorism programme, the court
OL,8,Fwas told.
OL,10,FIn 2021, when his school raised
OL,11,Fconcerns, a panel concluded his
OL,12,Fbehaviour was driven by autism rather
OL,13,Fthan ideological motivation after he
OL,14,Fsaid he no longer agreed with racist
OL,15,Fcomments he made when angry and denied
OL,16,Fbelieving the so-called Islamic State
OL,17,Fgroup was good.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FHe was referred to the programme again
OL,7,Fin May 2025, after reporting a desire
OL,8,Fto revert to Islam and speaking about
OL,9,Fthe Southport stabbings and Manchester
OL,10,FArena bombing.
OL,12,FHis referral was still being processed
OL,13,Fwhen he was arrested.
OL,15,FIn June that year he told a friend on
OL,16,FTikTok about the referral and said he
OL,17,Fhoped his case would be closed like
OL,18,FRudakubana's with "no clear ideology".
OL,26,@zD@SOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FPhilip Astbury, defending, said that
OL,7,Ffor some time before the incident the
OL,8,Fdefendant had been struggling with his
OL,9,Fmental health and spent "far too much
OL,10,Ftime sitting at a computer terminal".
OL,12,FThe 17-year-old denied a charge of
OL,13,Fmaking a threat to kill, which was
OL,14,Fordered to lie on the file.
OL,16,FThe Crown Prosecution Service said it
OL,17,Fwould not proceed with that charge and
OL,18,Fit will instead lie on the teenager's
OL,19,Ffile.
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772745126
OL,3,CTeen who wanted to copy Southport
OL,4,Cattacker avoids youth custody
OL,6,FBethan David, head of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service's counter-
OL,8,Fterrorism division, said: "This was a
OL,9,Fdeeply concerning case involving a
OL,10,Fyoung person who had been drawn
OL,11,Ftowards extreme and violent ideology,
OL,12,Fwith the potential for very serious
OL,13,Fharm."
OL,15,F"This case underlines the realworld
OL,16,Fconsequences of online radicalisation
OL,17,Fand the importance of early
OL,18,Fintervention. We continue to work
OL,19,Fclosely with partners such as Counter
OL,20,FTerrorism Policing to ensure that the
OL,21,Fpublic is protected."
OL,26,@pD@[OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
